## ðŸ”§ Troubleshooting

### Common Issues

**1. Images Not Loading**
- âœ… Check file paths are correct
- âœ… Verify assets folder exists
- âœ… Ensure file names match (case-sensitive)
- âœ… Fallback placeholders will show if missing

**2. Videos Not Playing**
- âœ… Add both MP4 and WebM formats
- âœ… Keep file sizes under 10MB
- âœ… Add `autoplay muted playsinline` attributes

**3. JavaScript Errors**
- âœ… Open browser console (F12)
- âœ… Check for typos in script.js
- âœ… Ensure jQuery is NOT required (vanilla JS)

**4. Mobile Menu Not Working**
- âœ… Test on actual mobile device
- âœ… Check console for errors
- âœ… Verify hamburger button has click listener

**5. Forms Not Submitting**
- âœ… Backend API must be configured
- âœ… Update action URLs in forms
- âœ… Test with console.log() first

**6. Slow Performance**
- âœ… Optimize all images (WebP/AVIF)
- âœ… Minify CSS/JS
- âœ… Enable Gzip compression
- âœ… Use CDN for assets

