## ðŸŽ¨ Customization Guide

### Change Color Scheme

Edit `styles.css` `:root` variables (lines 11-22):
```css
--navy-dark: #0a0e27;      /* Background */
--neon-cyan: #00d9ff;      /* Primary accent */
--neon-blue: #0080ff;      /* Secondary accent */
--gold-metallic: #ffd700;  /* Premium highlights */
```

### Change Fonts

Edit `index.html` Google Fonts link (line 17):
```html
<!-- Current fonts: Orbitron + Rajdhani -->
<!-- Replace with your choice from fonts.google.com -->
```

Then update CSS variables:
```css
--font-primary: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;   /* Headlines */
--font-secondary: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif; /* Body text */
```

### Adjust Glow Intensity

Edit in `styles.css`:
```css
--glow-cyan: 0 0 10px var(--neon-cyan), 
             0 0 20px var(--neon-cyan), 
             0 0 30px var(--neon-cyan);  /* Increase px for stronger glow */
```

### Add More Equipment/Trainers

Edit `script.js` data arrays:
- `equipmentData` (line 8)
- `trainersData` (line 88)
- `scheduleData` (line 151)
- `successStoriesData` (line 237)

